description:
This is a 8 minute workout called 'Best Workout To Build Muscle After 50 (Dumbbell Workout Over 50)' from the channel Live Anabolic.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.
